plots.content: Himegoto follows Hime Arikawa, a second-year student at Shimoshina High School (霜科高校, Shimoshina Kōkō?). Forced to assume a large amount of debt from his now-absent parents, Hime is saved by the three girls of his school's student council after he is chased down by debt collectors. In return for paying off his debt, Hime agrees to their conditions of becoming the student council's "dog" and spending his high school life dressed as a girl.

Arikawa Hime is a second-year student at Shimoshina High School. Forced to assume a large amount of debt left behind by his now-absent parents, Hime is saved by the three girls of his school's student council after he is chased down by debt collectors. In return for paying off his debt, Hime agrees to their conditions of becoming the student council's "dog" and spending his high school life dressed as a girl.Source: Wikipedia

Hime Arikawa is being pursued by debt collectors due to his absent parents mounting debts. The student council saves him on the condition that he becomes their toy and cross-dresses as a girl. The whole student body takes notice and some of them get in on the act.
